<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Register</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="form-container">
        <p>1. panjang karakter email min 10 karakter dan max 15 karater</p>
        <p>2. username mengandung format email (@)</p>
        <p>3. password harus mengadnung kombinasi karakter angka, symbol, huruf capital dan huruf kecil</p>
        <br>
        <h2>Register</h2>
        <form action="/api/v1/users/register" method="POST">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="email">email:</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Enter your email" required autocomplete="off">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="password">Password:</label>
                <input type="password" name="password" id="password" placeholder="password" required>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Register</button>
        </form>
        <p>Have an account? <a href="/login">Login</a></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>